response.overview: Woody has always been confident about his place in the world and that his priority is taking care of his kid, whether that's Andy or Bonnie. But when Bonnie adds a reluctant new toy called "Forky" to her room, a road trip adventure alongside old and new friends will show Woody how big the world can be for a toy.
response.tagline: Get ready to hit the road!
response.title: Toy Story 4

titles.title: ทอย สตอรี่ 4
